Use Case 08

CHARACTERISTIC INFORMATION
Goal in Context
As a statistician, I want to be able to see a report of the number of people who speak the following languages from greatest number to smallest,
including the percentage of the world population: Chinese, English, Hindi, Spanish, Arabic.
Scope
Company.
Level
Primary task.
Preconditions
We know the role. Database contains current country, city and population data .
Success End Condition
A report is available for statistician.
Failed End Condition
No report is produced.
Primary Actor
Statistician .
Trigger
A request for language information is sent to statistician.
MAIN SUCCESS SCENARIO
Population information is requested.
Statistician extracts report of I want to be able to see a report of the number of people who speak the following languages from greatest number to smallest,
                                including the percentage of the world population: Chinese, English, Hindi, Spanish, Arabic.
Statistician provides report.
EXTENSIONS

SUB-VARIATIONS
None.
SCHEDULE
DUE DATE: Release 2.0